Javier's coming.

18:10.872 --> 18:13.004
Shoot, all the guys
on the Island are coming.

18:13.179 --> 18:14.136
- Wow. Okay.
- Yeah.

18:14.310 --> 18:15.572
- Fun.
- Yeah.

18:17.661 --> 18:19.315
You seem better.

18:19.489 --> 18:22.275
Oh, well, you know,
I like a project.

18:25.016 --> 18:28.150
