and rather violent death.

24:54.231 --> 24:56.843
- Are you trying to scare me?
- Little bit.

24:57.017 --> 25:00.281
Well, no luck.
I am fearless now.

25:00.455 --> 25:01.587
Excellent.

25:01.761 --> 25:03.850
Anyway, that glowering
goth girl from the plane

25:04.024 --> 25:05.852
