32:50.272 --> 32:52.753
Your turn.

32:52.927 --> 32:54.973
Time to face your fear.

32:55.147 --> 32:58.193
The worst part is
I had this whole vision

32:58.367 --> 32:59.978
of how it was gonna be
meeting my dad.

33:00.152 --> 33:01.327
When I find him,

33:01.501 --> 33:04.373
he's gonna be happy
to know that I exist.

33:04.547 --> 33:06.593
I am so stupid.

33:06.767 --> 33:09.944
This island, it sucks.

33:10.118 --> 33:11.337
I'm sorry, Helene.

33:11.511 --> 33:13.730
Fantasy Island
delivers fantasies,

33:13.904 --> 33:15.602
not fairy tales.

33:15.776 --> 33:17.778
What you want and envisioned

33:17.952 --> 33:19.823
may be different
from what you need.

33:19.998 --> 33:22.130
What I need?

33:22.304 --> 33:24.350
I can't have what I need.

33:26.265 --> 33:28.702
I need my mom.

33:29.964 --> 33:33.141
God, she gave the best hugs.

33:33.315 --> 33:34.925
You know, when she hugged me,

33:35.100 --> 33:38.581
I just knew that
everything was gonna be okay.

33:38.755 --> 33:41.149
I sound so stupid because
it's not even possible,

33:41.323 --> 33:42.759
but I need a hug.

33:44.500 --> 33:46.589
I need a mom hug.

33:50.071 --> 33:51.855
Come with me.

33:52.030 --> 33:55.511
Oh, God.
Where are you taking me?

33:55.685 --> 33:57.296
Where you need to go.

34:08.002 --> 34:09.612
Ms. Roarke?

34:11.658 --> 34:14.226
Hey.

34:14.400 --> 34:16.924
Where did you come from?
Are you okay?

34:17.098 --> 34:19.187
Come here.

34:19.361 --> 34:21.146
Everything's gonna be okay.

34:24.714 --> 34:26.151
It's gonna be okay.

34:29.545 --> 34:33.984
I know it's scary,
but you're gonna be okay.

34:36.422 --> 34:39.642
Let's go.
It's not safe here.

34:39.816 --> 34:44.691
Hey, Blue, this way.
I found shelter.

34:44.865 --> 34:46.475
Come on!

34:46.649 --> 34:49.174
Hurry, I found somewhere safe.
Let's go.

35:06.408 --> 35:09.281
♪ I wish I could swoop you ♪

35:09.455 --> 35:13.763
♪ Into my wings ♪

35:13.937 --> 35:17.724
♪ But I'm just a songbird
outside your window ♪

35:17.898 --> 35:20.422
- Would you like me to...
- No, I...

35:20.596 --> 35:21.728
I need to do this on my own.

35:21.902 --> 35:24.296
♪ I wish I could
come inside ♪

35:24.470 --> 35:28.778
♪ And sit on your table ♪

35:28.952 --> 35:32.782
♪ Just spend the morning
talking and laughing ♪

35:36.221 --> 35:37.744
♪ And I'm singing ♪

35:37.918 --> 35:40.007
- Hi.
- Hey.

35:40.181 --> 35:43.793
♪ Trying to get through ♪

35:43.967 --> 35:46.622
♪ But you'll never
understand me ♪

35:46.796 --> 35:49.712
♪ So I'll sit here
and sing songs for you ♪

35:49.886 --> 35:51.540
It's Helene, right?

35:51.714 --> 35:54.152
Yeah, yeah,
I was named after a hurricane.

35:54.326 --> 35:56.763
No kidding.

35:56.937 --> 36:00.245
I was in the jungle
during Hurricane Helene.

36:02.377 --> 36:05.772
I didn't think I'd survive.

36:05.946 --> 36:06.642
In fact, I...

36:09.428 --> 36:11.691
I've carried this with me
ever since that night.

36:11.865 --> 36:13.736
Never forget it.

36:13.910 --> 36:16.043
St. Christopher's pendant
for protection.

36:17.958 --> 36:19.525
Yeah.

36:19.699 --> 36:21.918
Got us through the hurricane.

36:22.092 --> 36:23.964
I figured it must work.

36:26.706 --> 36:28.838
Um...

36:29.012 --> 36:32.886
I think that might've been
a gift from my mom.

36:35.845 --> 36:36.759
Blue.

36:36.933 --> 36:40.502
♪ Trying to get through ♪

36:40.676 --> 36:42.939
♪ But you'll never
understand me ♪

36:43.113 --> 36:45.638
♪ So I'll sit here
and sing songs for you ♪

36:45.812 --> 36:48.902
Blue... is your mom.

36:54.690 --> 36:56.214
It's nice to meet you, Helene.

37:00.522 --> 37:02.350
Would it be okay if...

37:05.092 --> 37:07.486
I hugged you?

37:07.660 --> 37:09.705
♪ But I'm just a songbird ♪

37:09.879 --> 37:11.794
♪ Tapping on your window ♪

37:15.929 --> 37:20.368
♪ I wish I could speak
in whatever language you do ♪

37:23.066 --> 37:27.027
♪ Spend the morning
talking and laughing ♪

37:30.073 --> 37:33.120
♪ I'm singing at
the top of my lungs ♪

37:33.294 --> 37:37.733
<i>♪ Trying to get through ♪</i>

37:37.907 --> 37:39.822
<i>♪ But you'll never
understand me ♪</i>

37:39.996 --> 37:43.652
<i>♪ So I'll sit here
and sing songs for you ♪</i>

37:43.826 --> 37:45.785
<i>♪ I ♪</i>

37:49.223 --> 37:53.183
<i>♪ Ooh, ooh, I ♪</i>

38:05.587 --> 38:07.763
You know what?
Why the hell not?

38:12.072 --> 38:13.595
It's a cleansing ceremony.

38:31.352 --> 38:35.878
Isla, hi.
- Hi, Ruby.

38:36.052 --> 38:37.750
Where did you come from?

38:37.924 --> 38:40.143
I heard you were
looking for me.

38:40.318 --> 38:44.626
Yeah, well, we had a guest
that needed a tattoo and...

38:44.800 --> 38:46.541
It's perfect.

38:49.936 --> 38:53.156
Did you know
when you gave it to me

38:53.331 --> 38:55.376
what it meant?

38:55.550 --> 38:57.639
I knew it was important.

38:57.813 --> 39:00.076
That you were...

39:00.250 --> 39:03.253
are special.

39:08.650 --> 39:10.391
I have to go,

39:10.565 --> 39:14.569
but I swim here often at night.

39:14.743 --> 39:17.137
I hope to see you soon again.

39:20.923 --> 39:21.620
Isla.

39:39.812 --> 39:41.291
Can we talk?

39:48.864 --> 39:50.953
Best bachelor party ever.

39:51.127 --> 39:52.781
- Agreed.
- You slayed it.

39:52.955 --> 39:56.002
- Oh.
- Good luck to all of you.

39:56.176 --> 39:57.612
And thank you.

39:57.786 --> 40:01.311
- And thank you, extra.
- Oh, you bet.

40:02.312 --> 40:03.836
You know what?

40:04.010 --> 40:07.535
There is man out there
just for you, okay?

40:07.709 --> 40:09.319
Just let me know
when you find him.

40:09.494 --> 40:10.190
Hmm?
- Yeah.

40:24.247 --> 40:26.946
- Jeez, he is in a hurry.
- Let's wait a second.

40:31.951 --> 40:34.475
- Morning.
- Hey.

40:34.649 --> 40:38.000
- Can I get your bag?
- No.

40:38.174 --> 40:40.916
Oh, right.
Only daughter of a single mom.

40:41.090 --> 40:42.657
I didn't bring it.

40:44.833 --> 40:47.575
Uh, Ms. Roarke said
that I could stay awhile.

40:51.405 --> 40:53.581
If that's okay with you.

40:53.755 --> 40:56.454
Yeah, that's more than okay.

40:59.108 --> 41:00.109
This doesn't mean
we're gonna be all

41:00.283 --> 41:01.981
father and daughter-y
and stuff.

41:02.155 --> 41:02.808
I just...

41:04.984 --> 41:07.552
I figured we might as well
get to know each other.

41:09.336 --> 41:11.207
How about lunch later?

41:12.861 --> 41:14.559
I'd like that. Yeah.

41:16.299 --> 41:17.649
Cool.

41:19.346 --> 41:22.349
- All right.
- All right, I'll see you.

41:32.620 --> 41:35.101
Thank you.

41:35.275 --> 41:36.624
Thank you.

41:36.798 --> 41:38.670
I, uh, I wanted to ask her,

41:38.844 --> 41:40.889
but she just found out
I'm her dad.

41:41.063 --> 41:42.543
I didn't want to overstep.
Freak her out.

41:42.717 --> 41:44.589
So I overstepped for you.

41:44.763 --> 41:47.200
Did you know
when she got here?

41:47.374 --> 41:50.072
- No idea.
- I'm sorry, I just feel like

41:50.246 --> 41:53.293
I'm missing out
on something big.

41:53.467 --> 41:54.947
I'll let her explain.

41:59.473 --> 42:01.606
Um...

42:01.780 --> 42:04.347
I don't even know
where to begin.

42:04.522 --> 42:07.133
Sounds like a job
for a pitcher of mimosas.

42:08.961 --> 42:11.180
Definitely.

42:11.354 --> 42:16.446
I think life is about to get...
interesting on Fantasy Island.

42:16.621 --> 42:19.101
This is gonna be good.
